    <p>{`To install it, either copy it to `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`.zshrc`}</inlineCode>{` or `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`.zprofile`}</inlineCode>{` or  a little cleaner  source this script in either of those files. For instance, say you have a `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`~/scripts`}</inlineCode>{` directory where you keep custom scripts like this, simply run`}</p>
